---

<footer class="ft ff-dots--inverse">
  <div class="ft__term">
    <div class="ft__bar">
      <span class="ff-live-dot"></span>
      <span style="margin-left:8px">ff://threat-feed</span>
      <span class="ft__bar-live">SIG LIVE · Δt 00:00:12</span>
    </div>
    <pre class="ft__pre"><span class="c"># {new Date().toISOString().replace('T', ' ').slice(0, 19)} UTC</span>
<span class="k">INFO</span>   <span class="s">Firewall Flamingos</span>  threat-intelligence · security-research
<span class="k">FEED</span>   reverse-engineering · AI × security · CVE analysis
<span class="c">› reading the adversary's mind, one binary at a time.</span></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="ft__cols">
    <div>
      <div class="ff-eyebrow">Reading</div>
      <a href="/blog/">Archive</a>
      <a href="/blog/">Writing</a>
      <a href="/knowledge_base/">Knowledge Base</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="ff-eyebrow">Elsewhere</div>
      <a href="/feed.xml">RSS · /feed.xml</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/vladburch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub · @vladburch</a>
      <a href="/search/">Search</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="ff-eyebrow">Subscribe</div>
      <p class="ft__sub-desc">A terse digest. Findings only, no hype. No tracking.</p>
      <div class="ft__form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="you@domain.tld" aria-label="Email address" />
        <button class="btn btn--sig btn--sm">Subscribe</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ft__base">
    <div>© MMXXVI FIREWALL FLAMINGOS · SOLO OPERATOR</div>
    <div>
      PGP D9FF·3BFF·4D3D ·
      <span style="color:var(--ff-signal)">signed</span> ·
      <span style="color:var(--ff-verify)">sealed</span> ·
      <span style="color:var(--ff-alarm)">exploitable</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .ft {
    margin-top: var(--s-9);
    background: var(--bg-inverse-1);
    color: var(--fg-inverse-1);
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 1.2px, transparent 1.2px);
    background-size: 14px 14px;
    padding: 56px 28px 28px;
  }

  .ft__term {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    background: #121214;
    border: 1px solid #1f1f23;
    border-radius: var(--r-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .ft__bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1f1f23;
    background: var(--bg-inverse-1);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ff-graphite-20);
    gap: 0;
  }

  .ft__bar-live {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ff-graphite-50);
  }

  .ft__pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ff-graphite-20);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .ft__pre .k { color: var(--ff-signal); }
  .ft__pre .s { color: var(--ff-verify); }
  .ft__pre .c { color: var(--ff-graphite-50); }
  .ft__pre .bad { color: var(--ff-alarm); }

  .ft__cols {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1f1f23;
  }

  .ft__cols .ff-eyebrow {
    color: var(--ff-graphite-50);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .ft__cols a {
    display: block;
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--fg-inverse-2);
    transition: color var(--dur-fast);
  }

  .ft__cols a:hover {
    color: var(--ff-white);
  }

  .ft__sub-desc {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--fg-inverse-2);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ft__form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ft__form input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--bg-inverse-1);
    border: 1px solid #26262b;
    border-radius: var(--r-2);
    color: var(--ff-white);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color var(--dur-fast);
  }

  .ft__form input:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--ff-signal);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .ft__base {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--ff-graphite-50);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ft__cols {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ft {
      padding: 40px 20px 24px;
    }
    .ft__cols {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .ft__base {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
